    <para id="import-auto-id1164135347452">
      <emphasis effect="bold">At 4 K and 14 T, σ</emphasis>
      <emphasis effect="bold">xy</emphasis>
      <emphasis effect="bold"> increases in quantized steps as researchers sweep the</emphasis>
