      <emphasis effect="bold">Figure 25.  Schematic illustration of bilayer graphene with a bottom gate  controlling the carrier concentration and an extra top gate. The distance between layers 1 and 2 is d ≈ 0.334 nm, and the potential diference is determined from eFd. F</emphasis>
